,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"如果你想移民係唔使續BNO"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:35:33.000Z","msg":"過得去唔係都打算移民咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 意思係5+1 之後可以用 BNO 過返黎香港咁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"移民英國係唔使持有效既BNO, 你用特區護照去到英國都可以即時申請居留5+1. <br />\n<br />\n即係你為移民英國係唔使續，但你為去旅行出咗事可以搵英國大使館求救，就要續BNO."},{"pid":"43439db27853aa0707b8c9c329ae234b22b9e5d5","tid":2138282,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ce59874e59cf0009f77fdc92d2a2fd3425aba61","tid":2138282,"uid":74816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92dd61dd00d680f696dc350b75f0c42ad9b94291","tid":2138282,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2e8328535d83633e02e7f35cec960715190a089","tid":2138282,"uid":74816,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:30:44.000Z","msg":"我遞信既意思係申請BNO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ok 我用錯字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"如果你想移民係唔使續BNO"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:35:33.000Z","msg":"過得去唔係都打算移民咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 意思係5+1 之後可以用 BNO 過返黎香港咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:00:39.000Z","msg":"突發!!! 英國政府己出了BNO VISA 基本資料<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/british-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fguidance%2Fbritish-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=735432e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/guidance/british-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n重點:<br />\n1) 2021年1月可以申請<br />\n2) 可以在英國境內申請<br />\n3) 簽證期: 30個月簽証, 之後再續30個月, 或一次性5年期簽證<br />\n4) 可以工作或讀書, 但不可以申請Public Fund<br />\n5) 居住滿5年後, 可以申請永居, 12個月後可以申請入籍<br />\n<br />\n申請條件:<br />\n1) 要有BNO資格 (己過期或遺失都可以)<br />\n2) 居住在香港<br />\n3) 有居住/財政證明至少夠在英國生活6個月<br />\n4) 承諾會學習英文<br />\n5) 要有肺結核健康證明<br />\n6) 支付IHS 費用<br />\n<br />\n若BNO VISA 申請人可以帶同以下家人:<br />\n1) 配偶<br />\n2) 未婚伴侶<br />\n3) 18歲以下小朋友 (首次申請時未滿18歲)<br />\n4) 其他家庭成員, 要證明高度依賴BNO VISA 申請人"},{"pid":"778e3852bc6cf9ace3e58c9bc4257da2eb09fc31","tid":2138282,"uid":53524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79fad3ccfba993d8d3b625dd1e9705e626d4735a","tid":2138282,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43439db27853aa0707b8c9c329ae234b22b9e5d5","tid":2138282,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ce59874e59cf0009f77fdc92d2a2fd3425aba61","tid":2138282,"uid":74816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92dd61dd00d680f696dc350b75f0c42ad9b94291","tid":2138282,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"如果你想移民係唔使續BNO"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:35:33.000Z","msg":"過得去唔係都打算移民咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 意思係5+1 之後可以用 BNO 過返黎香港咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:00:39.000Z","msg":"突發!!! 英國政府己出了BNO VISA 基本資料<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/british-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fguidance%2Fbritish-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=735432e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/guidance/british-nationals-overseas-in-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n重點:<br />\n1) 2021年1月可以申請<br />\n2) 可以在英國境內申請<br />\n3) 簽證期: 30個月簽証, 之後再續30個月, 或一次性5年期簽證<br />\n4) 可以工作或讀書, 但不可以申請Public Fund<br />\n5) 居住滿5年後, 可以申請永居, 12個月後可以申請入籍<br />\n<br />\n申請條件:<br />\n1) 要有BNO資格 (己過期或遺失都可以)<br />\n2) 居住在香港<br />\n3) 有居住/財政證明至少夠在英國生活6個月<br />\n4) 承諾會學習英文<br />\n5) 要有肺結核健康證明<br />\n6) 支付IHS 費用<br />\n<br />\n若BNO VISA 申請人可以帶同以下家人:<br />\n1) 配偶<br />\n2) 未婚伴侶<br />\n3) 18歲以下小朋友 (首次申請時未滿18歲)<br />\n4) 其他家庭成員, 要證明高度依賴BNO VISA 申請人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"仲有 18 - 23 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWe do not wish to split family units where there are dependent children over the age of 18, given the particular challenges linked to the timing of obtaining BN(O) status. In compelling and compassionate circumstances, we will therefore use discretion to grant a visa to the children of a BN(O) citizen who fall into this category and who are still dependent on the BN(O) citizen. We will limit this discretion ordinarily to children of BN(O) citizens who were born after the 1 July 1997 who will also be able to apply as dependants, if one of their parents holds BN(O) status and they apply together as a family unit."},{"pid":"01fc8bc9abc5820f96e3e45a577a10e2d0870a7e","tid":2138282,"uid":175659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"黎緊九月匯豐同大新停止匯款英鎊去境外<br />\n有冇人知係咪姐係針對證明自己要有足夠生活費呢一點，其實係咪要有英國戶口裡面有足夠英鎊先得"},{"pid":"794c4d905d02b3654e6bf01cd01d5c6e8842b659","tid":2138282,"uid":74816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:59:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3c8cbbba0e470fef72019f967fae7c1530fd4ba","tid":2138282,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"今日有更新<br />\n<br />\n3 August 2020<br />\nUpdated to <strong>advise</strong> families to travel to the UK together <strong>before</strong> the Hong Kong BN(O) Visa is available."},{"pid":"8ee1780629bf921ceeaf1bda1b66472129117535","tid":2138282,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3c8cbbba0e470fef72019f967fae7c1530fd4ba","tid":2138282,"uid":97181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"今日有更新<br />\n<br />\n3 August 2020<br />\nUpdated to <strong>advise</strong> families to travel to the UK together <strong>before</strong> the Hong Kong BN(O) Visa is available."},"ci